p_tmed_1=autoplot(tmed_1)+xlab("Ao")+ylab("Temperatura media [C]")+ggtitle("Temperatura media C3 - Cundinamarca del mes: Enero",subtitle = "Periodo 1981-2020 Fase: Senescencia y Cosecha")+ geom_line(aes(y=tmed_1,colour="T. media C"))  + geom_line(aes(y=16,colour="T. limite C"))+ scale_colour_manual("", values=c("T. media C"="black", "T. limite C"="red"))
